{"tid":2301326,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"淚吐變性手術後遺症！河莉秀「差點輕生」　身體不如八旬母","createTime":"2020-11-26T08:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T09:13:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f487448afbae46e051101c55956117c13d533824","tid":2301326,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"現年45歲的南韓女星河莉秀因擁有天使般的俏麗臉蛋加上魔鬼般的火辣身材，被稱作是「最美變性人」。近日她坐客脫口秀《Video Star》透露了因為小時候接受了變性手術，所以讓她提前經歷到更年期，由於荷爾蒙的劇烈的變化，讓她情緒非常不穩定，最嚴重的時候，還有過輕生的衝動，一席言論嚇壞現場眾人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/26/2902677-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F26%2F2902677-PH.jpg&h=ef1c29a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲河莉秀被譽為「最美變性人」。（圖／翻攝自河莉秀IG）<br />\n<br />\n河莉秀在2007年與小5歲的Micky鄭（鄭英鎮）步入禮堂，這段婚姻雖然維持了10年，但最終仍以失敗收場，她表示自己在離婚單身後，也努力瘦身想要變美，但運動後覺得膝蓋實在太痛了，就去醫院做檢查，結果被診斷出「骨質疏鬆」，骨密度竟然比她的八旬老母親還要低，「因為我很年輕就動了變性手術，加上頻繁減重，又跳舞跟穿高跟鞋」，對身體造成了相當嚴重的後遺症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/26/2902678-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F26%2F2902678-PH.jpg&h=7ce4dd6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲河莉秀曝變性手術後遺症。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<br />\n此外，她也提到自己在全盛時期，曾經在一日跑2場活動就可以賺到1億韓圜（約新台幣300萬元），不過也曾在每個月租金15萬（約新台幣4500元）的小窩住過，甚至當時連要交出這15萬都很辛苦，也因為這樣現在很常幫忙那些無家可歸的孤兒們，而現在她也想要展現自己以前活力十足的模樣，好好地生活下去。"},{"pid":"3e43d9a45c6d2bf8564770b6dbc224ac4b8c2339","tid":2301326,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"靚過彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e453a166a32e5d0f32f98f1f28865d79980d7d","tid":2301326,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e43d9a45c6d2bf8564770b6dbc224ac4b8c2339","tid":2301326,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"靚過彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f316401a00acf57d3d8844668c7854201dc5665f","tid":2301326,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"很勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48db720756dae2a83bfb8afdf37b4a236ca2e03","tid":2301326,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"整過龍"},{"pid":"2abee40764ddfd87f5c68a27048c89fa3d55ba02","tid":2301326,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f316401a00acf57d3d8844668c7854201dc5665f","tid":2301326,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"很勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"是勇者不必怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea6c7d947bb9f25510537aba8ac73f199d2c10e","tid":2301326,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"個樣俾車輾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\